{
    "publish_date": "2012-11-23T17:06:50.000Z", 
    "video_length": "PT14M12S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "A big part of why I work\nwith endangered languages,", 
            "dur": "3.268", 
            "start": "8.216"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is because I am myself\na descendant of a speech community", 
            "dur": "3.486", 
            "start": "11.508"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that even today\nis struggling to survive.", 
            "dur": "2.18", 
            "start": "15.018"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Look at the name over there,", 
            "dur": "1.267", 
            "start": "17.222"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you can probably guess\nwhich one it is.", 
            "dur": "2.231", 
            "start": "18.513"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But, for many of my friends,", 
            "dur": "2.157", 
            "start": "21.253"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "language loss\nis much more immediate,", 
            "dur": "1.79", 
            "start": "23.434"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "much more intense.", 
            "dur": "1.492", 
            "start": "25.248"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "For them, it&#39;s loss of a chunk\nof their sovereignty.", 
            "dur": "3.788", 
            "start": "26.764"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "A connection to their past.", 
            "dur": "1.738", 
            "start": "31.252"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "A connection to their cultural wealth.", 
            "dur": "2.211", 
            "start": "33.014"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "A grounding in their history.", 
            "dur": "2.275", 
            "start": "35.249"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In my work, I&#39;ve seen\ntime and time again,", 
            "dur": "3.301", 
            "start": "38.484"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "just how wrenching it can be", 
            "dur": "2.972", 
            "start": "42.255"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "for parent and child,", 
            "dur": "2.24", 
            "start": "45.251"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a grandparent and a grandchild,", 
            "dur": "1.728", 
            "start": "47.515"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to become disconnected\nin a way that goes", 
            "dur": "2.214", 
            "start": "49.267"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "far beyond any kind\nof natural generation gap.", 
            "dur": "3.037", 
            "start": "51.505"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But even if you care,", 
            "dur": "1.717", 
            "start": "56.502"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "even if you sympathize,\nyou may think,", 
            "dur": "2.254", 
            "start": "58.243"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;Well, endangered languages\njust aren&#39;t worth saving.&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.955", 
            "start": "60.521"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because you probably think\nthey&#39;ll cost a fair bit to save.", 
            "dur": "4.275", 
            "start": "63.5"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Not just money,\nbut also time, energy and attention.", 
            "dur": "3.776", 
            "start": "69.258"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And these are things\nthat&#39;re all in short supply these days.", 
            "dur": "2.431", 
            "start": "73.058"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Especially so for a lot\nof these communities,", 
            "dur": "2.659", 
            "start": "75.513"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "which are often faced with\neven more immediate,", 
            "dur": "2.349", 
            "start": "78.196"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "even more material challenges.\nBut what if it cost next to nothing?", 
            "dur": "4.909", 
            "start": "80.569"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Next to nothing\nto learn a new language?", 
            "dur": "2.726", 
            "start": "85.502"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What if we could radically reduce", 
            "dur": "1.972", 
            "start": "88.252"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "linguistic entry costs?", 
            "dur": "1.533", 
            "start": "90.248"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Well then the arguments\nagainst sustaining linguistic diversity,", 
            "dur": "3.498", 
            "start": "92.241"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "would not sound so reasonable.", 
            "dur": "1.974", 
            "start": "95.763"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because all of us", 
            "dur": "1.233", 
            "start": "97.761"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "could easily jump\nfrom language to language,", 
            "dur": "2.456", 
            "start": "99.018"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "just to show respect\nto our host or our guest.", 
            "dur": "2.232", 
            "start": "101.498"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Or to enjoy the expressive capacities", 
            "dur": "1.998", 
            "start": "103.754"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that this particular language allows us.", 
            "dur": "1.973", 
            "start": "105.776"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Or simply because between you and me,", 
            "dur": "2.956", 
            "start": "107.773"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "this language is the one\nI feel the most like home.", 
            "dur": "3.026", 
            "start": "110.753"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So the obvious question is,", 
            "dur": "1.285", 
            "start": "114.229"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "how long does it take\nto learn a new language?", 
            "dur": "2.227", 
            "start": "115.538"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Not perfectly,", 
            "dur": "0.973", 
            "start": "117.789"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "not you know, without a single error,", 
            "dur": "2.522", 
            "start": "118.786"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "not even fluently, but just enough\nto get your foot in the door.", 
            "dur": "3.019", 
            "start": "121.332"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Enough to get started,", 
            "dur": "1.088", 
            "start": "124.375"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to get going, enough to join\nthat speech community and be part of it.", 
            "dur": "3.735", 
            "start": "125.488"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Well, in my experience,", 
            "dur": "1.755", 
            "start": "129.247"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it&#39;s about a week or so.", 
            "dur": "1.498", 
            "start": "131.026"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And you know,", 
            "dur": "1.225", 
            "start": "133.274"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was just as shocked\nas you to discover this.", 
            "dur": "2.469", 
            "start": "134.523"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In the summer of 2003,\nafter just 10 days in Bulgaria", 
            "dur": "5.198", 
            "start": "137.016"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with my new in-laws,", 
            "dur": "0.98", 
            "start": "142.238"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was able to talk well enough", 
            "dur": "1.482", 
            "start": "143.242"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to translate for my sister when she came.", 
            "dur": "2.04", 
            "start": "144.748"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then the same thing happened\nagain the next summer.", 
            "dur": "2.64", 
            "start": "146.812"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I went to the Czech Republic\nfor my cousin&#39;s wedding,", 
            "dur": "2.221", 
            "start": "149.476"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "showed up about a week early,\nand by the time the wedding rolled around,", 
            "dur": "3.008", 
            "start": "151.721"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was just chatting away\nwith all my new Czech relatives.", 
            "dur": "2.772", 
            "start": "154.753"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I wasn&#39;t fluent and I wasn&#39;t flawless\nbut I was effective.", 
            "dur": "3.481", 
            "start": "158.255"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now real fluency, in my experience,", 
            "dur": "1.995", 
            "start": "161.76"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "does take a long time,", 
            "dur": "1.468", 
            "start": "163.779"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "does take hanging out\nwith the speech community.", 
            "dur": "2.446", 
            "start": "165.271"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But still, just one week and change", 
            "dur": "4.014", 
            "start": "167.741"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to get a foot in the door.", 
            "dur": "1.712", 
            "start": "171.779"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "To be able to party with the chicks.", 
            "dur": "1.697", 
            "start": "173.515"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "To be able to hang on Bulgarian cafes", 
            "dur": "1.75", 
            "start": "175.236"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and order French fries with aplomb.", 
            "dur": "1.774", 
            "start": "177.01"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That seemed like an idea worth sharing.", 
            "dur": "2.341", 
            "start": "179.994"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now of course,\nI&#39;m a trained field linguist,", 
            "dur": "2.12", 
            "start": "182.359"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so you probably think,\n&quot;You&#39;re self selected.", 
            "dur": "2.163", 
            "start": "184.503"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You&#39;ve got experience.\nYou&#39;ve got talent.&quot; Right?", 
            "dur": "3.047", 
            "start": "186.69"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But when I do it,", 
            "dur": "0.992", 
            "start": "189.761"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it doesn&#39;t feel at all like talent,", 
            "dur": "2.23", 
            "start": "191.503"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and not much like experience either.", 
            "dur": "1.72", 
            "start": "193.757"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "All it feels like is a really clear\nsense of what to do.", 
            "dur": "3.479", 
            "start": "195.501"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "How to handle vocabulary,\npronunciation, grammar,", 
            "dur": "2.968", 
            "start": "199.004"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and more than anything else,", 
            "dur": "1.33", 
            "start": "201.996"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "how to make it through any conversation.", 
            "dur": "2.207", 
            "start": "203.35"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And this is what I think we&#39;re missing", 
            "dur": "2.46", 
            "start": "207.74"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when we struggle with languages.", 
            "dur": "1.505", 
            "start": "210.224"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When we fall to learn languages.", 
            "dur": "2.188", 
            "start": "211.753"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We all get taught languages,", 
            "dur": "1.816", 
            "start": "214.241"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but we don&#39;t get taught\nhow to learn languages.", 
            "dur": "2.5", 
            "start": "216.081"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;ve been working on that\nfor quite some time.", 
            "dur": "2.38", 
            "start": "218.668"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "On how to translate the experience,", 
            "dur": "2.074", 
            "start": "221.073"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the skill set of a trained field linguist\ninto a form that anybody,", 
            "dur": "2.915", 
            "start": "223.171"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "any of you can pick up quickly", 
            "dur": "2.109", 
            "start": "226.11"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and use to become active learners,\nconfident learners,", 
            "dur": "3.476", 
            "start": "228.243"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "who can step right out into the street,\nthe scary street of real-life language use", 
            "dur": "5.998", 
            "start": "231.743"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with very little fear.", 
            "dur": "1.78", 
            "start": "238.501"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And if we can do this,", 
            "dur": "1.248", 
            "start": "241.191"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "then it doesn&#39;t just change", 
            "dur": "1.277", 
            "start": "242.463"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "how you and me learn languages,", 
            "dur": "1.982", 
            "start": "243.764"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but it also has the potential\nto radically reshape", 
            "dur": "2.707", 
            "start": "245.77"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "how linguistic majorities\nand linguistic minorities", 
            "dur": "3.99", 
            "start": "248.501"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "can live and work together\nin the same world.", 
            "dur": "2.175", 
            "start": "252.515"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because now,\nseparate linguistic traditions", 
            "dur": "2.488", 
            "start": "255.24"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "are no longer communicative obstacles,", 
            "dur": "1.972", 
            "start": "257.753"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but actually resources.", 
            "dur": "1.705", 
            "start": "259.749"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Social, cultural, intellectual,", 
            "dur": "2.262", 
            "start": "261.478"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "even emotional resources\nthat we can all share and enjoy together.", 
            "dur": "5.152", 
            "start": "263.764"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, how do we do it?\nHow do we get that foot in the door?", 
            "dur": "2.516", 
            "start": "269.265"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "At least that foot in the door.", 
            "dur": "1.398", 
            "start": "271.806"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "First and foremost,", 
            "dur": "1.267", 
            "start": "273.229"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "what we need to understand\nis our own psychology.", 
            "dur": "2.374", 
            "start": "274.521"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We need to understand that it&#39;s the social\nand the emotional aspects", 
            "dur": "3.241", 
            "start": "276.919"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of language learning\nthat decide everything.", 
            "dur": "1.958", 
            "start": "280.184"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because when we first start\nto learn a language,", 
            "dur": "2.056", 
            "start": "282.166"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it&#39;s humiliating.\nEmbarrassing. It&#39;s frustrating.", 
            "dur": "2.669", 
            "start": "284.246"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So this gets you guys all rushing\nat the door to go learn a language.", 
            "dur": "3.349", 
            "start": "287.735"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But this is because as adults,\nas teenagers,", 
            "dur": "2.659", 
            "start": "291.564"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we measure ourselves on how well\nwe can present ourselves with our words.", 
            "dur": "3.491", 
            "start": "294.247"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And in a new language\nwe lose that control,", 
            "dur": "2.024", 
            "start": "297.762"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and we run screaming away from that.", 
            "dur": "2.046", 
            "start": "299.81"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We dodge conversations.", 
            "dur": "1.476", 
            "start": "301.88"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We hide on a linguistic sideline.", 
            "dur": "1.61", 
            "start": "303.38"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We do anything to avoid\na simple face-to-face conversation,", 
            "dur": "2.784", 
            "start": "305.014"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "which is the one thing, the only thing\nthat&#39;s going to make us better.", 
            "dur": "3.217", 
            "start": "307.822"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And as English speakers in today&#39;s world,\nthe world is very accommodating of that.", 
            "dur": "3.904", 
            "start": "311.063"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It makes it very easy for us", 
            "dur": "1.711", 
            "start": "314.991"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to indulge in our instinct to just bailout", 
            "dur": "2.488", 
            "start": "316.726"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when we get linguistic stage fright.", 
            "dur": "2.297", 
            "start": "319.238"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So what do we do?", 
            "dur": "1.095", 
            "start": "322.275"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Well, the short answer is,", 
            "dur": "1.64", 
            "start": "323.395"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we learn to check our shame at the door.", 
            "dur": "2.229", 
            "start": "325.059"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We learn to embrace this loss of control,", 
            "dur": "2.273", 
            "start": "327.718"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "enjoy the fact that we&#39;ve been", 
            "dur": "1.708", 
            "start": "330.015"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "--more or less involuntarily--", 
            "dur": "1.458", 
            "start": "331.747"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "given a second childhood\nin a new language.", 
            "dur": "2.343", 
            "start": "333.229"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Right?", 
            "dur": "1.087", 
            "start": "336.252"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, if we can do this,", 
            "dur": "1.389", 
            "start": "339.966"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "then we have learned to shift our job,", 
            "dur": "2.994", 
            "start": "342.5"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "reframe our job.", 
            "dur": "1.951", 
            "start": "345.518"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "To not from trying to seek out perfection,", 
            "dur": "3.502", 
            "start": "347.493"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "not making any mistakes,", 
            "dur": "1.215", 
            "start": "351.019"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but instead, just learning to cope well.", 
            "dur": "2.26", 
            "start": "352.258"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And the best place to learn\nlinguistic coping skills", 
            "dur": "5.022", 
            "start": "355.208"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is through simply learning\nhow to improvise.", 
            "dur": "4.481", 
            "start": "360.254"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Learning how to use description,\nmetaphor, analogy.", 
            "dur": "3.973", 
            "start": "364.759"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "To work around the words\nthat we don&#39;t know.", 
            "dur": "2.123", 
            "start": "368.756"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So for example, if I don&#39;t know\nhow to say tiger in your language,", 
            "dur": "3.309", 
            "start": "370.903"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I will say, &quot;It&#39;s a thing,\nit&#39;s like a cat but big and orange,", 
            "dur": "4.502", 
            "start": "374.236"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and the one behind you\nlooks a little bit hungry.&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.729", 
            "start": "378.762"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "1.376", 
            "start": "381.515"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s these clunky\nbut effective descriptions", 
            "dur": "2.213", 
            "start": "383.282"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that actually get us through\nany conversation.", 
            "dur": "4.977", 
            "start": "385.519"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And when we learn\nto congratulate ourselves on them,", 
            "dur": "2.463", 
            "start": "390.52"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when we realize that,", 
            "dur": "1.47", 
            "start": "393.007"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;Wow, this person actually\nunderstood what I said,&quot;", 
            "dur": "3.103", 
            "start": "394.501"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "then we feel good about ourselves.", 
            "dur": "1.602", 
            "start": "397.628"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We find they understood what I said", 
            "dur": "2.478", 
            "start": "399.254"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and now, even better,", 
            "dur": "1.32", 
            "start": "401.756"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "they&#39;re telling me how to say it right.", 
            "dur": "1.935", 
            "start": "403.1"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That&#39;s a language lesson\nthat we will never ever forget.", 
            "dur": "2.88", 
            "start": "405.059"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Never.", 
            "dur": "1.026", 
            "start": "408.5"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, there&#39;s actually\na second lesson inside this,", 
            "dur": "2.935", 
            "start": "409.551"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "which is that, language \nis not all on you.", 
            "dur": "2.982", 
            "start": "412.51"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When you and I speak together,\nwe make meaning together.", 
            "dur": "3.228", 
            "start": "415.516"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So learning to cope well", 
            "dur": "1.191", 
            "start": "418.84"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in an another language,\nis as much, if not more,", 
            "dur": "2.448", 
            "start": "420.055"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "about learning to lean\non the other person&#39;s", 
            "dur": "2.214", 
            "start": "422.527"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "full and complete knowledge\nof the language", 
            "dur": "2.22", 
            "start": "424.765"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and even more\non their willingness to help you", 
            "dur": "3.232", 
            "start": "427.009"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "make this conversation happen.", 
            "dur": "2.029", 
            "start": "430.265"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So again,\nif we learn to reframe our task,", 
            "dur": "4.277", 
            "start": "432.744"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "reframe our job,", 
            "dur": "1.207", 
            "start": "437.045"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "as being effective, not perfect,", 
            "dur": "5.938", 
            "start": "438.276"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "then every conversation stops being\nthis potential minefield", 
            "dur": "3.233", 
            "start": "444.238"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of embarrassing mistakes and errors.", 
            "dur": "2.909", 
            "start": "447.495"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Instead, it&#39;s an exciting place\nfor us to come back to every time.", 
            "dur": "3.119", 
            "start": "450.428"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because you get to be your own MacGyver.", 
            "dur": "1.761", 
            "start": "453.571"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You get to rummage around\nin your linguistic pockets", 
            "dur": "2.187", 
            "start": "455.356"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and pull out a toothbrush,\na button and a paperclip,", 
            "dur": "2.454", 
            "start": "457.567"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and couple that all together", 
            "dur": "1.43", 
            "start": "460.045"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and somehow pull off\nthe communicative job.", 
            "dur": "3.217", 
            "start": "461.499"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Right?", 
            "dur": "1.078", 
            "start": "464.74"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When you feel that thrill\nof being a linguistic hero", 
            "dur": "2.604", 
            "start": "465.843"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "time and time again,", 
            "dur": "1.038", 
            "start": "468.471"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you come back to conversations,\nyou seek them out, you want to be there.", 
            "dur": "3.47", 
            "start": "469.534"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And when you approach\nthe task like that, well pretty soon,", 
            "dur": "3.71", 
            "start": "473.028"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you find yourself fairly close to fluent.", 
            "dur": "2.159", 
            "start": "476.762"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So that&#39;s how we cope\nwith linguistic stage fright.", 
            "dur": "4.375", 
            "start": "478.945"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "With linguistic performance anxiety.", 
            "dur": "1.849", 
            "start": "483.344"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Which is 90% of what holds us back.", 
            "dur": "2.529", 
            "start": "485.217"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The only thing left\nis of course the language.", 
            "dur": "2.746", 
            "start": "487.77"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "All the pronunciation.\nAll the grammar.", 
            "dur": "1.972", 
            "start": "491.026"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "All the vocabulary.", 
            "dur": "1.181", 
            "start": "493.022"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s really intimidating,\nbut mostly because", 
            "dur": "2.134", 
            "start": "494.227"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we&#39;re all trying to juggle it all at once.", 
            "dur": "2.099", 
            "start": "496.385"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We&#39;ve got no way to organize it.\nNo way to prioritize it.", 
            "dur": "2.77", 
            "start": "498.508"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There is a way.", 
            "dur": "1.292", 
            "start": "501.776"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What we need is a simple,\npractical understanding", 
            "dur": "4.649", 
            "start": "503.092"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of the design features of language.", 
            "dur": "2.23", 
            "start": "507.765"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So let me give you\njust a brief taste of that.", 
            "dur": "2.272", 
            "start": "510.019"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Take pronunciation.", 
            "dur": "1.744", 
            "start": "513.27"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Anybody can learn to pronounce\nany sound in any language of the world.", 
            "dur": "3.273", 
            "start": "515.038"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Anyone of you. All of you.", 
            "dur": "1.272", 
            "start": "518.335"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If you don&#39;t believe me,\nit&#39;s probably because", 
            "dur": "2.096", 
            "start": "519.631"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you&#39;ve heard the following phrase,\n&quot;Listen and repeat after me.&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.92", 
            "start": "521.751"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That doesn&#39;t work. It doesn&#39;t work.", 
            "dur": "2.088", 
            "start": "524.695"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What does work, is learning\nthe clear and simple set of instructions", 
            "dur": "3.474", 
            "start": "527.493"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "for how to move your mouth\nto make that weird sound.", 
            "dur": "2.502", 
            "start": "530.991"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "After that, all you need\nis a little bit of exercise", 
            "dur": "2.496", 
            "start": "533.517"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to work your mouth\nfor that oral choreography.", 
            "dur": "2.374", 
            "start": "536.037"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And very soon you find\nthat your muscles limber up.", 
            "dur": "2.432", 
            "start": "538.435"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And what have seemed unfamiliar,", 
            "dur": "1.577", 
            "start": "540.891"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "unpronounceable, unreachable even,", 
            "dur": "2.005", 
            "start": "542.492"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "becomes almost as familiar\nas every other sound", 
            "dur": "2.216", 
            "start": "544.521"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you have been saying your whole life.", 
            "dur": "1.738", 
            "start": "546.761"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So you don&#39;t need any special talent.", 
            "dur": "1.956", 
            "start": "548.523"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You don&#39;t need\nany special ear for language.", 
            "dur": "3.713", 
            "start": "550.503"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You just don&#39;t.", 
            "dur": "1.086", 
            "start": "554.24"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But even more importantly,", 
            "dur": "1.121", 
            "start": "555.351"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is rhythm and melody.", 
            "dur": "3.728", 
            "start": "556.496"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When you go after\nthe distinct cadence of language.", 
            "dur": "2.696", 
            "start": "560.248"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When you try to internalize that,", 
            "dur": "1.807", 
            "start": "562.968"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that particular languages uses,", 
            "dur": "2.264", 
            "start": "565.485"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and use that as the foundation\nof your own pronunciation,", 
            "dur": "2.737", 
            "start": "567.773"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "well then, it turns out that\nyour own words come out fluently.", 
            "dur": "4.227", 
            "start": "570.534"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They flow in that cadence.", 
            "dur": "1.308", 
            "start": "575.781"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The cadence is the current\nthat carries all your words.", 
            "dur": "2.668", 
            "start": "577.113"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Even better, when you&#39;ve internalized it", 
            "dur": "1.989", 
            "start": "579.805"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and you&#39;re waiting for it, expecting it,", 
            "dur": "1.932", 
            "start": "581.818"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "then suddenly, something almost\nmiraculous happens.", 
            "dur": "2.363", 
            "start": "583.774"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Which is that, native speaker speech", 
            "dur": "2.313", 
            "start": "586.161"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "suddenly doesn\u2019t seem so fast.", 
            "dur": "1.501", 
            "start": "588.498"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because it&#39;s that rhythm and that melody\nthat actually tells you", 
            "dur": "3.198", 
            "start": "590.023"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "where the words begin and end.", 
            "dur": "1.891", 
            "start": "593.245"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So that&#39;s pronunciation,\nbut what about grammar?", 
            "dur": "2.326", 
            "start": "595.16"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Grammar is terrifying. Right?", 
            "dur": "1.776", 
            "start": "597.51"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s only because we teach grammar", 
            "dur": "1.713", 
            "start": "599.746"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "as a million little disconnected\narbitrary single rules,", 
            "dur": "2.65", 
            "start": "601.483"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when in fact grammars\nare tiny little ecosystems.", 
            "dur": "2.312", 
            "start": "604.157"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Every little part\nfits into every little part.", 
            "dur": "2.133", 
            "start": "606.493"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And if we look at those\necosystems from the top,", 
            "dur": "2.266", 
            "start": "608.65"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we can see a very helpful simplicity,", 
            "dur": "1.784", 
            "start": "610.94"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "which is that, all of those rules", 
            "dur": "1.721", 
            "start": "612.748"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "fall down on one side or the other\nof what we do when we talk.", 
            "dur": "3.246", 
            "start": "614.493"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Which is, we mention general concepts.", 
            "dur": "2.469", 
            "start": "617.763"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Things like cat and dog.", 
            "dur": "1.768", 
            "start": "620.256"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Events like bite and chase. Right?", 
            "dur": "3.169", 
            "start": "622.048"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then we tie them into", 
            "dur": "1.734", 
            "start": "625.241"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the specifics of this conversation.", 
            "dur": "1.715", 
            "start": "626.999"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "My cat, your dog,", 
            "dur": "1.745", 
            "start": "628.738"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that bit me, in yesterday&#39;s past tense.", 
            "dur": "2.5", 
            "start": "630.507"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It turns out all grammatical rules\nactually fall somewhere along the line", 
            "dur": "3.566", 
            "start": "633.76"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "between the general conceptual\nand the conversation specific.", 
            "dur": "2.884", 
            "start": "637.35"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And once you play round\nwith this idea for a while,", 
            "dur": "2.31", 
            "start": "640.258"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "grammatical rules become\nextremely easy to remember.", 
            "dur": "2.51", 
            "start": "642.592"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because now you know\nwhere they live in the neighborhood", 
            "dur": "2.492", 
            "start": "645.126"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and what their relationships\nare to their neighbors.", 
            "dur": "2.452", 
            "start": "647.642"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "After that, the only thing\nthat&#39;s left is vocabulary.", 
            "dur": "3.03", 
            "start": "650.118"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Dictionaries full of all the words\nyou don&#39;t know yet.", 
            "dur": "2.614", 
            "start": "653.758"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But it turns out, we don&#39;t actually need\nto know that much vocabulary.", 
            "dur": "3.278", 
            "start": "656.396"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because we have our coping skills.", 
            "dur": "1.634", 
            "start": "659.699"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We can talk around the words\nthat we don&#39;t know.", 
            "dur": "2.176", 
            "start": "661.358"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We can listen, from context work out\na lot of the new words we&#39;re hearing.", 
            "dur": "4.183", 
            "start": "663.559"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And when all else fails,", 
            "dur": "1.432", 
            "start": "667.766"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "now we know we have license\nto simply ask for help.", 
            "dur": "3.146", 
            "start": "669.222"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So what words do we actually\nneed to learn first?", 
            "dur": "2.404", 
            "start": "673.498"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The short words.\nThe small words.", 
            "dur": "2.249", 
            "start": "678.232"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The little linking words.\n&quot;Thing&quot; is one of them.", 
            "dur": "2.363", 
            "start": "680.505"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The words like: and, or, but, of, the,\nwho, what, when, where and why.", 
            "dur": "4.756", 
            "start": "684.238"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because these&#39;ll get you\nthe most expressive bang for your buck.", 
            "dur": "3.018", 
            "start": "689.018"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "These&#39;re the words that&#39;ll save you\nwhen you need to deep in the conversation.", 
            "dur": "3.683", 
            "start": "692.06"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You know exactly what you want to say,", 
            "dur": "1.819", 
            "start": "695.767"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "then you hit this wall", 
            "dur": "1.129", 
            "start": "697.61"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because you realize you&#39;ve not learned\nthe word &quot;almost&quot;.", 
            "dur": "2.809", 
            "start": "698.763"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "1.965", 
            "start": "702.272"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When you focus on those words\nfrom the get-go,", 
            "dur": "2.216", 
            "start": "704.261"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you find you&#39;ve the frame,\nthe outlines of language up and running,", 
            "dur": "3.256", 
            "start": "706.501"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and then there&#39;s only one thing left:\nthe rest of the language.", 
            "dur": "2.994", 
            "start": "709.781"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And there&#39;s a trick for this.", 
            "dur": "2.315", 
            "start": "713.265"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "To prioritize the rest of vocabulary,", 
            "dur": "1.996", 
            "start": "716.21"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "get what you need first,", 
            "dur": "1.532", 
            "start": "718.23"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you can start with\nthe egocentric experience of the body.", 
            "dur": "2.932", 
            "start": "719.786"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You say okay, my eyes, they see.", 
            "dur": "1.978", 
            "start": "722.742"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They see and they look.\nMy ears, they listen and they hear.", 
            "dur": "3.007", 
            "start": "724.744"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "My hands, they pick up and put down.", 
            "dur": "1.81", 
            "start": "727.774"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "My mind, it knows, it feels,\nit loves, it understands,", 
            "dur": "3.767", 
            "start": "729.609"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and when it tries to learn a language,", 
            "dur": "1.872", 
            "start": "733.401"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "sometimes it remembers\nand sometimes it forgets.", 
            "dur": "2.342", 
            "start": "735.297"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When you get these words, these core\nverbs of interaction and experience,", 
            "dur": "4.341", 
            "start": "737.773"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and tie them together\nwith all those little linking words,", 
            "dur": "2.787", 
            "start": "742.138"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it&#39;s a very small set of vocabulary\nthat you actually know,", 
            "dur": "2.836", 
            "start": "744.949"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but it happens to be precisely", 
            "dur": "1.41", 
            "start": "747.809"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the set of expressive tools that you need\nto make your way through any conversation.", 
            "dur": "4.504", 
            "start": "749.243"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, I hope that I have convinced you", 
            "dur": "3.488", 
            "start": "754.737"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that this is not just for linguists.", 
            "dur": "2.984", 
            "start": "758.249"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Anybody can learn a language.\nAnybody can get that foot in the door,", 
            "dur": "3.231", 
            "start": "761.257"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "which is the part that really matters.", 
            "dur": "2.057", 
            "start": "764.512"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You can do it. Right here. Right now.", 
            "dur": "2.786", 
            "start": "767.479"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "All it really takes,", 
            "dur": "2.737", 
            "start": "771.505"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is a somewhat better sense\nof where our emotions are at.", 
            "dur": "3.856", 
            "start": "774.267"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Where our heart is at\nwhen we go to learn a language.", 
            "dur": "2.664", 
            "start": "778.148"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And also a better sense,", 
            "dur": "1.893", 
            "start": "780.837"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of how language actually\ndoes fit into our minds.", 
            "dur": "3.15", 
            "start": "782.754"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And if this is possible", 
            "dur": "1.205", 
            "start": "786.675"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it means that joining\na new speech community", 
            "dur": "2.104", 
            "start": "787.905"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is much easier than you think.", 
            "dur": "1.425", 
            "start": "790.033"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That can take a lot of the pressure off\nof the people who&#39;ve been told,", 
            "dur": "3.544", 
            "start": "791.482"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;You need to abandon your small language\nin favor of this big large language.&quot;", 
            "dur": "4.691", 
            "start": "795.05"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But there&#39;s more.", 
            "dur": "1.507", 
            "start": "800.711"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Every language that I have ever learned,", 
            "dur": "2.209", 
            "start": "802.242"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "every language\nthat I even started to learn,", 
            "dur": "2.894", 
            "start": "804.475"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "has radically reshaped\nhow I look at the world.", 
            "dur": "3.893", 
            "start": "807.393"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "How I deal with people.", 
            "dur": "1.95", 
            "start": "811.31"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "How I think. And that&#39;s lovely.", 
            "dur": "2.711", 
            "start": "813.284"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But even more important than that,\nare the people that I&#39;ve met,", 
            "dur": "3.216", 
            "start": "816.019"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and the ways I&#39;ve been able to meet them", 
            "dur": "2.222", 
            "start": "819.259"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because of learning their language.", 
            "dur": "1.951", 
            "start": "821.505"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They have changed my life", 
            "dur": "1.469", 
            "start": "823.48"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in more ways that I can even\nbegin to describe here.", 
            "dur": "2.73", 
            "start": "824.973"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Up till now, that kind of opportunities", 
            "dur": "2.489", 
            "start": "827.727"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "only have been available\nto trained linguists", 
            "dur": "2.532", 
            "start": "830.24"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and the occasional genius savant polyglot.", 
            "dur": "3.678", 
            "start": "832.796"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But now, we all have the meat.", 
            "dur": "3.263", 
            "start": "836.498"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And so there&#39;s nothing more\nI can say, except, go for it.", 
            "dur": "3.215", 
            "start": "839.785"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Good luck.", 
            "dur": "1.001", 
            "start": "843.024"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Applause)", 
            "dur": "2.73", 
            "start": "844.049"
        }
    ], 
